  {
    "id": "TALK_bandit_rs_bomber_mission2",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": "Everything is ready, <name_g>.  I was able to get close enough to them, now there was only one small step.  The problem is that as soon as I open the passage for them, they will pour out of there like ants from their hive.  It would be nice to put a few guys here so that they shoot them, but for some reason no one agreed.  Now I sit here, waiting for something.",
